title: Debunking the Biggest Myth About Stan Lee?
description:
Delve into the perspectives shared by Abraham Riesman, author of 'True Believer: The Rise and Fall of Stan Lee,' as we unravel the myth of Lee being a far-left activist. Is the great Stan Lee truly the progressive hero many want him to be? Or was he more of an enlightened centrist?

#stanlee #marvelcomics #truebeliever
